Merafe Resources Posts Annual Earnings Per Share of 11 Cents

-- B y   A n t o n y   S g u a z z i n
-- 
2011-03-01T06:02:16Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-01/merafe-resources-says-it-returned-to-profit-in-12-months-through-december.html
  Merafe Resources Ltd . said it posted
annual earnings per share of 11 South African cents compared
with a loss of 6 cents the year earlier.  Merafe commented in a statement to the Stock Exchange News
Service in Johannesburg today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
